{"tid":839306,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美證監起訴特斯拉CEO馬斯克涉證券欺詐","createTime":"2018-09-28T00:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-28T00:24:31.000Z","uid":28765,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"8fd07f2c9f9878cadd92ac9029b5ad994067fae3","tid":839306,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:13:39.000Z","msg":"美國證券交易委員會(SEC)在美股收市後公布，起訴電動車生產商特斯拉(Telsa)行政總裁馬斯克(Elon Musk)證券欺詐罪。<br />\n<br />\n消息公布前，特斯拉股價在尾段滑落，收市跌0.7%。SEC公布後，該公司在市後時段再挫逾6%。<br />\n<br />\nSEC向紐約南法院提交起訴書，針對馬斯克早前在社交媒體發文，提出有意把公司私有化，並稱資金已備妥的言論。起訴書指控馬斯克當時實際上沒有具體談論私有化細節以及資金來源。因此，SEC要求禁止馬斯克出任公司董事或管理人員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1955056/%E7%BE%8E%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89CEO%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%B6%89%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Finternational%2Farticle%2F1955056%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E8%25AD%2589%25E7%259B%25A3%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E8%25A8%25B4%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%2596%25AF%25E6%258B%2589CEO%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E6%2596%25AF%25E5%2585%258B%25E6%25B6%2589%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B8%25E6%25AC%25BA%25E8%25A9%2590&d=bJhAS8wAitB51WKrMcBxzKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=e075e0c5\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/international/article/1955056/%E7%BE%8E%E8%AD%89%E7%9B%A3%E8%B5%B7%E8%A8%B4%E7%89%B9%E6%96%AF%E6%8B%89CEO%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%B6%89%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E6%AC%BA%E8%A9%90</a>"},{"pid":"b6042126155f9bf3bc4e8283886ff6f5d2e5121c","tid":839306,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-28T00:24:31.000Z","msg":"玩大左啦條友"}]}